"{\"uid\": \"havanatimes.org-diaries-kamil-kenders-an-olympic-return-trip\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  By Kamil Kenders  HAVANA TIMES - Now back in my Havana, and recovered from an exhausting trip, I can detail how difficult it was to return from Bayamo, Granma.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\", \"score\": 0.9707381090555921, \"rank\": 0.030143959787243546, \"text\": \"Kamil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\"}, {\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"score\": 0.9999999997310169, \"rank\": 2.0252751921058663e-10, \"text\": \"Havana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\"}, {\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Granma_Province\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.403534776025554e-13, \"text\": \"Granma\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Granma_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Granma_Province\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Considering that interprovincial transportation gets worse during vacations, I can still say that the mafia that exists to obtain a ticket is immense.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First attempt at a ticket: Failed.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We dismissed the normal route because there is no point in trying to get a ticket through the app created for it.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first mafia begins there when you see that there is space on a bus, and in less than a minute, there are no more seats.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why does this happen?\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's because there are people buying up the tickets at the established price (a little over 200 pesos) to then resell them for over 3,000 pesos.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Attempt number 2: Outside the Bayamo bus terminal (like in all provinces), there are\\\"bukenkes\\\"(those are the people who shout out the destinations of the buses and cars outside the establishment).\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The price of these tickets ranges between 4,500, 5,000, and 6,000 pesos, depending on the size, type of bus, distance, and comfort.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thebukenkeshave some sort of arrangements with the bus drivers, so each one of them, with every ticket, gets a good slice of that money.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In summary, it took me two days to leave Bayamo and return to Havana on a bus with decent conditions.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"score\": 0.9999999997310169, \"rank\": 2.0252751921058663e-10, \"text\": \"Havana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I left on a Sunday at five in the afternoon and arrived in Havana the next day, twelve hours later, which is how long it takes for a bus to cover 840 km.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"score\": 0.9999999997310169, \"rank\": 2.0252751921058663e-10, \"text\": \"Havana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was left wanting to return to Bayamo, but it will not be for a long time because, honestly, a lot, a lot of money is needed just for transportation, plus the stress caused by the uncertainty of whether you will be able to travel or not.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more from the diary of Kamil Kenders here.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1748, \"end\": 1753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\", \"score\": 0.9707381090558128, \"rank\": 0.030143959787243546, \"text\": \"Kamil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al-Kamil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2025 Havana Times Photo Contest AnnouncementSee now\\u2026  Copyright \\u00a9 2025Havana Times.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1776, \"end\": 1788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Havana Times\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havana_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}]}"